First import the CAD FILE AS IT IS FROM DESIGN SOFTWARE 
DELETE ALL THE CURVES AND POINTS AFTER IMPORTING  WHICH IS RECOMMENDED FOR BETTER GEMOTRY
THEN APPLY BUILD TOPOLOGY WHICH WILL AUTOMATICALLY GENERATE THE REQUIRED SURFACES   AND CURVES FOR MESHING AS PER THE TOLORENCE SPECIFIED BY USER
COLOUR SSYTEM IN ICEMCFD
    1. GREEN = UNCONNECTED
    2. YELLOW = SINGLE OR SURFACE IS MISSING OR GAP IS GRATED THEN TOLORENCE APPLIED, NEED TO BE FIXED
    3. RED = DOUBLE
    4. BLUE= MULTIPLE 
    5. GRAY = FILTERED OUT
